<H3>Abstract</H3>
<P>This memo presents a technique for using XML (Extensible Markup =
Language) as=20
a source format for documents in the Internet-Drafts (I-Ds) and Request =
for=20
Comments (RFC) series. </P><A name=3Dtoc>
