<H3>4.&nbsp;Security Considerations</H3>
<P>This memo raises no security issues; however, according to <A=20
href=3D"http://memory.palace.org/authoring/writing-rfcs.html#refs.RFC2223=
">[2]</A>,=20
your document should contain a section near the end that discusses the =
security=20
considerations of the protocol or procedures that are the main topic of =
your=20
document, e.g., </P></FONT><PRE>    &lt;middle&gt;
        ...
        &lt;section title=3D"Security Considerations"&gt;
            &lt;t&gt;This memo raises no security issues;
            however,
            according to &lt;xref target=3D"refs.RFC2223" /&gt;,
            your document should contain a section near the end
            that discusses the security considerations of the
            protocol or procedures that are the main topic of your
            document.&lt;/t&gt;
        &lt;/section&gt;
    &lt;/middle&gt;
</PRE><FONT face=3D"verdana, helvetica, arial, sans-serif" size=3D2><A=20
name=3Drfc.references><BR>
